  "name": "Onyx",
  "profile": "Hiphop group hailing from Queens New York.\r\nPut on by [a=Jam Master Jay] in the early 90's Onyx had massive success on the Hiphop scene with their \"Bacdafucup\" LP and the huge singles \"Slam\" and \"Throw Ya Gunz\".\r\nThey released more records as a group and members Sticky Fingaz and Fredro Starr have gone on to some solo success, Fredro as an actor in the TV-Show \"Moesha\" which also featured [a=Brandy (2)].",
